      "updatedAt": 1780931719536,
      "html": "\n      <header class=\"site-header\">\n        <a class=\"brand\" href=\"index.html\" aria-label=\"AI DRI 指南针首页\">\n          <span class=\"brand-mark compass-mark\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n            <svg viewBox=\"0 0 44 44\" role=\"img\">\n              <circle cx=\"22\" cy=\"22\" r=\"18\"></circle>\n              <path d=\"M26.8 17.2 23.9 29l-6.7-2.2 2.9-11.8 6.7 2.2Z\"></path>\n              <path d=\"M20.1 15 17.2 26.8l6.7 2.2 2.9-11.8-6.7-2.2Z\"></path>\n              <path d=\"M22 5v5M22 34v5M5 22h5M34 22h5\"></path>\n            </svg>\n          </span>\n          <span>AI DRI 指南针</span>\n        </a>\n        <nav class=\"nav\" aria-label=\"主导航\">\n          <a data-nav-key=\"guide\" href=\"guide.html\">核心概念</a>\n          <a data-nav-key=\"map\" href=\"map.html\">能力地图</a>\n          <a data-nav-key=\"cases\" href=\"cases.html\">常见误区</a>\n          <a data-nav-key=\"resources\" href=\"resources.html\">成长路径</a>\n          <a data-nav-key=\"about\" href=\"index.html#about\">关于我们</a>\n        </nav>\n        <div class=\"editor-bar\" aria-label=\"编辑工具栏\">\n          <button class=\"editor-button editor-primary\" type=\"button\" id=\"toggleEdit\">编辑模式<span aria-hidden=\"true\">›</span>\n          </button>\n          <button class=\"editor-button\" id=\"saveLocal\" type=\"button\">保存本机</button><button class=\"editor-button\" type=\"button\" id=\"savePage\">发布云端</button>\n          <button class=\"editor-button\" id=\"refreshCloud\" type=\"button\">从云端刷新</button><button class=\"editor-button\" type=\"button\" id=\"exportHtml\">导出 HTML</button>\n          <button class=\"editor-button\" id=\"cloudSettings\" type=\"button\">GitHub 已连接</button><span class=\"save-status\" id=\"saveStatus\" aria-live=\"polite\"></span>\n        </div>\n      </header>\n\n      <main id=\"top\">\n        <section class=\"hero\" aria-labelledby=\"hero-title\">\n          <div class=\"hero-copy\">\n            <p class=\"pill\">AI 时代能力升级</p>\n            <h1 id=\"hero-title\">从会用 AI，<br>到成为 AI 时代的 DRI</h1>\n            <p class=\"hero-text\">\n              AI 时代的 DRI，不是把任务交给 AI 的人，而是能真实业务目标和价值为\n              AI 明确边界、可评估、可迭代，并产生可沉淀资产和复利效应的人。\n            </p>\n            <p class=\"hero-text\">&nbsp;</p>\n            <div class=\"hero-actions\">\n              <a class=\"button primary\" href=\"#dri\">开始导览 <span aria-hidden=\"true\">→</span></a>\n              <a class=\"button secondary\" href=\"#assessment\">先做自测</a>\n            </div>\n            <a class=\"scroll-hint\" href=\"#assessment\">\n              <span aria-hidden=\"true\">↓</span>\n              往下滚动查看更多\n            </a>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"hero-media single-media\" aria-label=\"AI DRI 能力地图图片区\">\n            <article class=\"hero-visual-card\">\n              <img data-editable-image=\"\" src=\"assets/home-hero.gif\" alt=\"AI DRI 问题定义导览动效\">\n            </article>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"assessment\" class=\"assessment section-card\" aria-labelledby=\"assessment-title\">\n          <div class=\"section-heading\">\n            <h2 id=\"assessment-title\">先做一个 AITI 人格测试</h2>\n            <p>回答 10 个场景题，生成你的 AI DRI 人格画像。</p>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"quiz-stage\">\n            <button class=\"round-nav prev\" type=\"button\" id=\"prevQuestion\" aria-label=\"上一题\">←</button>\n            <article class=\"quiz-card ghost left\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <p>第 10 / 10 题</p>\n              <h3>当 AI 能力要从 Demo 走向稳定复用时，你会优先补什么？</h3>\n            </article>\n\n            <article class=\"quiz-card active\" aria-live=\"polite\">\n              <p class=\"quiz-count\" id=\"quizCount\">第 1 / 10 题</p>\n              <h3 id=\"quizQuestion\">场景：业务同学提出“能不能用 AI 做一个自动生成短视频脚本的功能”，希望你当天给出初步判断。你最可能先怎么做？</h3>\n              <div class=\"options\" id=\"quizOptions\"></div>\n            </article>\n\n            <article class=\"quiz-card ghost right\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <p>第 2 / 10 题</p>\n              <h3>一个 AI Demo 看起来效果不错，准备上线前你最关注什么？</h3>\n            </article>\n            <button class=\"round-nav next\" type=\"button\" id=\"nextQuestion\" aria-label=\"下一题\">→</button>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"quiz-dots\" id=\"quizDots\" aria-label=\"题目进度\"></div>\n          <article class=\"quiz-result\" id=\"quizResult\" aria-live=\"polite\" hidden=\"\">\n            <div class=\"result-medal\" aria-hidden=\"true\">✦</div>\n            <div>\n              <p class=\"result-kicker\">AITI 人格已生成</p>\n              <h3>你的 AITI 人格：<span id=\"resultLevel\">选型者 × 操盘手 × 流程师 × 主导型 DRI</span></h3>\n              <p id=\"resultCopy\">\n                完成 10 道题后，将展示四层能力标签、核心能力得分、长板与短板。\n              </p>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"dri\" class=\"dri-section section-card\" aria-labelledby=\"dri-title\">\n          <div class=\"section-heading\">\n            <h2 id=\"dri-title\">DRI 到底是什么</h2>\n            <p>这一份专门澄清误区</p>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"definition-grid\">\n            <article class=\"definition-panel negative\">\n              <h3><span aria-hidden=\"true\">×</span> DRI 不是</h3>\n              <ul>\n                <li>仅用 AI 工具的人</li>\n                <li>会写 Prompt 的人</li>\n                <li>被动 Demo 的人</li>\n                <li>把任务交给模型就完事的人</li>\n                <li>模仿最佳实践的人</li>\n              </ul>\n            </article>\n\n            <div class=\"definition-arrow\" aria-hidden=\"true\">····→</div>\n\n            <article class=\"definition-panel positive\">\n              <h3><span aria-hidden=\"true\">✓</span> DRI 是</h3>\n              <ul>\n                <li>能定义真实业务问题的人</li>\n                <li>能拆解 AI 最适合介入的人</li>\n                <li>能制定假设、设定可量化 KPI 的人</li>\n                <li>能设计 Agent 或工作流的人</li>\n                <li>能评估产出、发现价值偏差的人</li>\n                <li>能复盘迭代、复利沉淀的人</li>\n              </ul>\n              <div class=\"definition-tags\" aria-label=\"定义详情\">\n                <button type=\"button\" class=\"tag-popover tag-row-1\" data-popover=\"problem\">问题定义</button>\n                <button type=\"button\" class=\"tag-popover tag-row-2\" data-popover=\"collab\">AI 协同素养</button>\n                <button type=\"button\" class=\"tag-popover tag-row-4\" data-popover=\"agent\">Agent 应用力</button>\n                <button type=\"button\" class=\"tag-popover tag-row-5\" data-popover=\"evaluate\">评估 / 优化</button>\n                <button type=\"button\" class=\"tag-popover tag-row-6\" data-popover=\"launch\">上线迭代</button>\n              </div>\n            </article>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"core-definition\">\n            <span aria-hidden=\"true\">★</span>\n            <strong>核心定义</strong>\n            <p>AI 时代 DRI = 对 AI 价值闭环直接负责的人</p>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"resources\" class=\"why-section section-card\" aria-labelledby=\"why-title\">\n          <h2 id=\"why-title\">为什么需要这套指南针</h2>\n          <div id=\"about\" class=\"faq-list\">\n            <details>\n              <summary><span>给你一个真实的用户反馈（来自一增长方向 PM 的分享）</span><span class=\"faq-plus\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span></summary>\n              <p>真正有用的 AI 指南针，不是告诉你会用什么工具，而是帮助你判断自己在业务、技术、落地和提效中的真实位置。</p>\n            </details>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n      </main>\n\n    ",
